room_title: Escape room "Mafia Mayhem" by Escape Reality Games in Sarasota
room_address: 6250 N Lockwood Ridge Rd Sarasota, FL 34243
room_description:
Go back to the Roaring Twenties and visit the streets of New York in search of a good time. With Prohibition in full swing, it can be tough to spend the night out, but we know a guy who knows a guy...
The Speakeasy experience includes an adult beverage served to you by your in-room gamemaster/bartender. Just don't tell the coppers!
